    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i cant just \"live with it.\" that sounds so exhausting. how can anyone just pretend everything is okay when everything is actually ruined? it feels like there's no real solution, just different ways to suffer. like... is there really any other way to actually find peace than just letting go of it all?",
